article.description: — Jhamir Brickus registered 14 points as La Salle edged past Army 61-58 on Saturday.
article.headline: La Salle holds off Army 61-58
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Jhamir Brickus registered 14 points as La Salle edged past Army 61-58 on Saturday. Khalil Brantley had 12 points for the Explorers (2-2). Christian Ray added 10 points and eight rebounds. Clifton Moore blocked six shots. Jalen Rucker had 13 points and six rebounds for the Black Knights (3-2). Charlie Peterson added 13 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
